                  %h4.panel-title Am I "fit" enough to CrossFit?
              #collapseOne.panel-collapse.collapse
                .panel-body.text-left
                  YES! The needs of Olympic athletes and our grandparents differ by degree not kind. The CrossFit program is designed for universal scalability making it the perfect application for any committed individual regardless of experience. We’ve used our same routines for elderly individuals with heart disease to Firefighters, Military, Law enforcement, elite athletes, and everyone in between! We scale load and intensity; we don’t change programs.
            .panel.panel-default
