                  %p NO! For our female athletes, please check out this awesome article from CFFMS about CrossFit and bulkiness. 
                  %p= link_to 'ARTICLE', "https://crossfitfms.wordpress.com/2012/07/20/the-fear-of-bulkiness-and-crossfit", :target => "_blank", class: "btn btn-success btn-sm faq-button reduce"
